<Retconned>

Basically, if Nocterrans are "purple jackals", Caithians are "green cats". They're inspired by the cait sith of old folklore and little green men of ufology. Their eyes... the sentence was intended to read as "two big eyes surrounded by several smaller ones", but it's been interpreted as "eyes with slit pupils surrounded by smaller eyes", meaning literally eyes within eyes. Others still have interpreted them with compound eyes. I'm not sure which design I like best, but I'm leaning towards either compound or multi-eyes. Whichever appeals to you better works! Like I said I'm just honored you think enough of my work to consider drawing characters from it! If there's anything else you wanna know, fire away, my friend.
